<!-- ============================================================
  THE CHALLENGE (light bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label">The Challenge</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>15 Years of Excellence, Zero Online Visibility</h2>
        <p>
          BuildRight Infra had built a solid reputation in Gandhinagar over 15 years. Their residential projects in Sector 21 and commercial builds near GIFT City were spoken about positively by clients who had worked with them. Rajan Mehta, the director, had grown the firm almost entirely on referrals and government tenders.
        </p>
        <p>
          The problem was that a new generation of property developers and homeowners in Gandhinagar do not call a builder based on a neighbour's recommendation alone. They search Google, compare options, check Google reviews, and fill out a contact form. BuildRight Infra did not exist in any of those places. Their website had been built in 2016, had no SSL certificate, was not mobile-friendly, and had no contact form that actually worked.
        </p>
        <p>
          Rajan came to us after losing a Rs. 1.5 crore residential contract to a competitor he knew did inferior work. That competitor had a modern website, active Google Business Profile, and ranked first for "construction company Gandhinagar." The buyer had searched online, found the competitor, and never even considered calling BuildRight Infra because they could not find them.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-challenge-list">
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Completely invisible in search results</strong>
              <p>Not ranking for a single construction-related keyword in Gandhinagar or Ahmedabad, including their own business name</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>No Google Business Profile</strong>
              <p>No GBP listing at all, so they did not appear in local map results where most construction searches happen</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Website built in 2016, non-functional on mobile</strong>
              <p>No SSL, no mobile layout, broken contact form, and no project portfolio to show completed work</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-challenge-item">
            <span class="cs-challenge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>No lead tracking or attribution</strong>
              <p>Could not measure which channels brought inquiries, making it impossible to know where to invest marketing spend</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  OUR APPROACH (dark bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-two-col">
      <div class="cs-section-label-col">
        <span class="section-label light">Our Approach</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-section-body">
        <h2>Fix the Foundation First. Then Spend on Ads.</h2>
        <p>
          Construction is a trust-intensive industry. Before we ran a single rupee in ad spend, we needed a website that could convert the traffic we were about to send. A strong ad campaign sending leads to a broken 2016 website would have wasted every rupee. We fixed the foundation first.
        </p>

        <div class="cs-process-steps">
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">01</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Website Rebuild with Project Portfolio</h4>
              <p>Rebuilt the website from scratch with a clean, professional layout. Added a project portfolio section with completed residential and commercial builds in Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad. Every page had a working contact form and click-to-call button for mobile users.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">02</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Google Business Profile Setup</h4>
              <p>Created and fully optimised the Google Business Profile with verified address, project photos, service categories, Q&amp;A entries, and a review collection process. Within 6 weeks they were appearing in the local map pack for Gandhinagar construction searches.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">03</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Local SEO for 20+ Target Keywords</h4>
              <p>Built location-specific service pages targeting "construction company Gandhinagar," "builder Sector 21," "residential construction GIFT City," and 17 other high-intent keywords. On-page SEO, LocalBusiness schema, and consistent NAP citations across all relevant directories.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">04</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Google Ads Campaigns with ₹40,000/Month Budget</h4>
              <p>Launched search campaigns targeting property developers, homeowners planning construction, and commercial developers in the Gandhinagar-Ahmedabad corridor. Tightly themed ad groups, location bid adjustments for GIFT City and key Gandhinagar sectors, and negative keyword lists to eliminate irrelevant clicks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-step">
            <div class="cs-step-num">05</div>
            <div class="cs-step-content">
              <h4>Lead Tracking Dashboard and Monthly Reporting</h4>
              <p>Set up call tracking, form submission tracking, and a monthly reporting dashboard showing leads by source, cost per lead, and project inquiry value. Rajan now knows exactly which keywords and campaigns are generating his best leads each month.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
  WHAT WE BUILT (light bg)
============================================================ -->
<section class="cs-section cs-light">
  <div class="container">
