              <p>Location-specific pages targeting Gandhinagar, GIFT City, and Sector 21 searches. Full LocalBusiness schema, Google Business Profile optimisation, and 15+ local directory citations for consistent NAP data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📢</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Google Ads Campaigns (₹40,000/mo)</h4>
              <p>Search campaigns targeting construction buyers in Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad corridor. Separate campaigns for residential and commercial. Monthly budget managed, optimised, and reported with full transparency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">⭐</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Google Business Profile Setup</h4>
              <p>Full GBP creation and optimisation with project photos, service listings, Q&amp;A, and post updates. Review request process set up as part of every completed project handover.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📊</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Lead Tracking Dashboard</h4>
              <p>Google Analytics 4 with goal tracking for form submissions and call clicks. Monthly report showing leads by source, cost per lead by campaign, and estimated project value of inquiries received.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📋</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Monthly Performance Reports</h4>
              <p>Written monthly summary with rankings, lead count, ad spend breakdown, cost per lead, and recommendations for the following month. Delivered by the 5th of each month without needing to ask.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
