    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label light">The Results</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:white;">Numbers That Speak for Themselves</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">Measured at the 4-month mark. Lead data verified via call tracking and form submission logs. Rankings via Google Search Console.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-results-grid">
      <div class="cs-result-card cs-result-accent">
        <div class="cs-result-number">8x</div>
        <div class="cs-result-label">ROI on Google Ads Spend</div>
        <div class="cs-result-note">₹40,000 monthly ad spend generating project inquiries worth Rs. 2.4 crore in the first 6 months alone.</div>
